text: St Peter & St Paul, Teddington is an Anglican parish church at Bychurch End in Teddington, in the London Borough of Richmond upon Thames. It is in close cooperation with the Church of St Mary with St Alban, and they share the same clergy. The Reverend Joe Moffatt is the Priest-in-Charge. ==References== ==External links== *History of the church Teddington Category:Diocese of London Category:History of the London Borough of Richmond upon Thames
